# Match Coins Game

This project is an object-oriented Python game for Lab 9.

## Description

The game creates two players. Each player has a wallet of coins and a coin object. Each round, both players toss their coins. If the coins match, Player 1 wins a coin. If the coins do not match, Player 2 wins a coin.

## Files

- `coin.py`: Contains the Coin class.
- `player.py`: Contains the Player class.
- `Lab9_amedina6-1.py`: Runs the main game logic.

## OOP Concepts Used

- Classes
- Objects
- Private attributes
- Methods
- Composition
- Modules and imports

## How to Run

bash terminal 
python Lab9_amedina6-1.py